## Team process plate (other skills)

**What this section is:** How someone in *another* repo copies this pattern—where the template file lives and what to read next. Paths below assume **`parts/process.md`** at the skill root; if your file is **`content/parts/process.md`**, use **`../../templates/…`** instead of **`../templates/…`**.

To author a **rich** **`process.md`** (outcome, principles, per-stage tables), start from **[templates/process-team.md.template](../templates/process-team.md.template)** and **[templates/README.md](../templates/README.md)**.
